            <h1 style="text-align: center; font-size: 3em;">OUR VISION</h1>
            <hr style="border-color: white;">
            <p>Our vision is to bridge the gap between the number of people who need organs
                and
                the number of people who
                donate organs. We want to ensure that the maximum number of people pledge their organs for donation. We
                also
                aim to make the process of organ transplantation smoother and faster.</p>
